                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Reflection</h5>
                                        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">After the circle, groups identify common themes and present 3 key learnings about indigenous knowledge transmission to the wider community.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                `
            },
            reciprocity: {
                title: "Reciprocity Web",
                content: `
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <div class="bg-earth/10 rounded-2xl p-6 border-l-4 border-earth">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Learning Objective</h4>
                            <p class="text-charcoal/70">Understand the indigenous principle of reciprocity through experiential group activity, moving beyond transactional thinking to relational exchange.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-3 flex items-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-earth"></i>
                                    Duration
