                                <p class="text-charcoal/70">75 minutes</p>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-3 flex items-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="users" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-earth"></i>
                                    Group Size
                                </h4>
                                <p class="text-charcoal/70">6-10 participants</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-4">Activity Flow</h4>
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-earth text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold">1</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">The Gift Exchange (20 min)</h5>
                                        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Each participant brings a small, meaningful object. They offer it to someone in the group with an explanation of its significance. The receiver must accept and later pass it on with added meaning.</p>
