                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-earth text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold">2</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Web Building (25 min)</h5>
                                        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Using yarn, participants physically create a web by connecting gifts and givers. Each connection represents a relationship of obligation, gratitude, and ongoing responsibility.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                                    <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-earth text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 font-bold">3</div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h5 class="font-semibold text-charcoal">Reflection (15 min)</h5>
                                        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Discuss: How does this differ from buying/selling? What are the obligations created by receiving? How does this mirror ecological relationships?</p>
