                                        <p class="text-charcoal/60 text-sm">Groups present their webs and explain the concept of "all my relations" and how reciprocity functions in indigenous stewardship of resources.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                `
            }
